Posts.Content: Thanks for your response! I did call my clinic and set up an appointment for next Monday, I will let you know how things go, I'm sure everything is just fine. Good luck with your treatments, after seeing my mom go through everything it just amazes me what the human body and spirit can overcome, you’re in my prayers! Thanks again,
Posts.Title: Should i See a Doctor?

Posts.Content: I have found a less than pea sized bump on my inner middle right breast, not really any pain, and I am only 30, if the skin is stretched you can see the bump, no redness or irritation to the skin or any other problems, don’t want to seem like a hypochondriac, do have breast cancer in my family, a mom and great-grandmother, both diagnosed in their 40s, any insight would be helpful as I don’t really feel that there is a lump, just more like a bump?
